_sText:
This is yet another recreation of the popular map cs_crackhouse. This version is based on the CS:S version, not the original CS 1.6 version as I've never played it.

All of the other recreations have some little quirk in them I did not like. I did not like the day lighting, alternate routes or portions added in, or they just edited the decompiled original map to make it look better. This is a complete recreation from scratch, using measurements from the original (rounded to the nearest power of 2, of course).

I believe this is the first crackhouse map to use HDR, so that should be a big plus. The bots only get stuck on the rarest of occasions, due to me editing the nav. Place names, overviews, more detail, soundscapes, etc. Basically, this is what cs_crackhouse SHOULD have been, if it had been made better.

Anyway, hope you enjoy!
